                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yehwa ika kich..., chi..., kipahtiah yo:n seki, tein, tein ta..., neli kineltokah, tein a:mo pos a:mo, iwki a. Ke:mah.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
